        "content": "<p>I'm working through <em>Theorem Proving in Lean</em> and I'm finding that I have to convert from ¬¬p to p often. Is there a convenient shorthand or do I always have to do something like</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hnnp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">¬¬</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Classical</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">not_not</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hnnp</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">--Do something with hp to produce False</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 533126577,
        "sender_full_name": "Ada Weird",
        "timestamp": 1754493824
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Not really, except maybe omitting the <code>Classical</code> if you had mathlib.</p>",
        "id": 533126887,
        "sender_full_name": "Robin Arnez",
        "timestamp": 1754493952
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>there is <code>of_not_not hnnp</code> in Mathlib</p>",
        "id": 533127061,
        "sender_full_name": "Kenny Lau",
        "timestamp": 1754494015
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hnnp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">¬¬</span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hnnp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">p</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">--Do something with hp to produce False</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
